body:
This mod includes two rings, the Ring of Flight and the Advanced Ring of Flight;

The base ring uses XP as fuel, gives passive fall damage resistance if you have xp, can be enchanted with the Unbreaking enchantment (each level grants a 20% chance to not remove one point of XP, can't be obtained via the Enchantment Table) and can be upgraded to the Advanced ring of flight in a smithing table with an Elytra.

![Ring of Flight | Advanced Ring of Flight](https://i.imgur.com/JJYqfCK.png)
